high_descs: Turn right and begin walking to the oven, then hang a right and walk up to where the toaster is on the counter and look up.
Open the rightmost cupboard door and remove the large golden spoon with a blue handle.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left again and walk up to the oven and turn right to face it.
Place the large golden spoon into the frying pan on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the frying pan with the large golden spoon inside of it.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk around to the far side of the kitchen island.
Place the metal frying pan with the spoon in it onto the island in between the two glasses.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a spoon in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the kitchen toaster on your right, then look up at the cabinet above
grab a spoon out of the cabinet above
look back down, then take a left and walk to the end of the room, then take a left and walk over to the stove on your right
place the spoon on the sauce pan on the stove
grab the sauce pan off of the stove with the spoon in it
turn around and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room, then turn right and walk over to the middle of the kitchen island on your right
place the sauce pan down on the kitchen island behind the glass on your right
anns.task_desc: place a sauce pan with a spoon in it down on the kitchen island counter top

high_descs: Turn around and go to the cabinet above the toaster.
Open the cabinet on the right and take out the ladle.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the ladle in the frying pan on the stove.
Pick up the frying pan on the stove.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the frying pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the frying pan from the stove to the table.

high_descs: Turn around to the counter with the toaster.
Open the cabinet above and remove the laddle, shut the door.
Carry the laddle and turn around and to the right to go to the stove.
Place the laddle in the pan on the back of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Carry the pan and turn around go right around to the other side of the island.
Place the pan and laddle on the right side of the island.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and laddle to the island.

high_descs: Walk to your right, then face right towards the kitchen cabinet
Open the rightmost kitchen cabinet then pick up a measuring cup from in the cabinet
Turn around and approach the stove from the front
Place the measuring cup in the frying pan
Pick up both the frying pan and the measuring cup that is in it
Turn around and approach the kitchen table from the side near the wall
Place the frying pan and measuring cup on the kitchen table to your right
anns.task_desc: Pick up two cooking instruments and place them on a kitchen table
